text: The ukulele is a small stringed instrument with four strings. Ukulele may also refer to: * Cliff Edwards, known as "Ukulele Ike", an American singer * "Ukulele Lady", a song by Gus Kahn and Richard A. Whiting * Ukulele Baby!, an album by The Wiggles * Several orchestras: ** Langley Ukulele Ensemble ** New York Ukulele Ensemble ** Ukulele Orchestra of Great Britain ** Wellington International Ukulele Orchestra * Ukulele (Taiwanese band), a Taiwanese pop duet * Yooka-Laylee, a 2017 3D platform game
title: Ukulele (disambiguation)
